o help you reach out to them?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 10:37:29',0),(375,'user','I can\'t take it anymore','depression','2025-03-25 10:38:04',0),(376,'assistant','Hi John Doe, I\'m here to listen. Can you tell me more about what\'s been going on?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 10:38:15',0),(377,'user','Sadness is overpowering','depression','2025-03-25 10:38:20',0),(378,'assistant','I understand that sadness can be overwhelming. What specifically has been contributing to your feelings of sadness?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 10:38:32',0),(379,'user','My terrible academic performance. I feel like a waste to human society','depression','2025-03-25 10:38:45',1),(380,'assistant','It sounds like you\'re putting a lot of pressure on yourself, John Doe. Remember, everyone faces challenges in their studies. Can you tell me more about what\'s been going on academically?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 10:38:58',0),(381,'user','I can\'t get good marks. I have a CPI of 3.1','depression','2025-03-25 10:39:13',0),(382,'assistant','Your CPI is just one measure of your worth, John Doe. There are many other aspects that define you as an individual. Have you considered exploring extracurricular activities or seeking support from your professors?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 10:39:28',0),(383,'user','Not really','depression','2025-03-25 10:39:32',0),(384,'assistant','Exploring new avenues might help shift your focus and provide a sense of accomplishment outside of academics. What are some hobbies or interests that you have, John Doe?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 10:39:43',0),(385,'user','I like painting','normal','2025-03-25 10:39:49',0),(386,'assistant','That\'s wonderful! Painting can be a great outlet for emotions. Have you considered joining an art club or taking up painting classes to further develop your skills and connect with others who share the same interest?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 10:40:11',0),(387,'user','not yet','extreme','2025-03-25 10:40:15',0),(388,'assistant','Exploring these possibilities might bring some joy