ou tell me more about what\'s been causing your anxiety?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:20:29',0),(402,'user','My exams are coming up, and I dont think I am prepared','depression','2025-03-25 14:20:41',1),(403,'assistant','I understand how that can be overwhelming. What specific subjects or topics are making you feel unprepared?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:20:52',0),(404,'user','Formal languages and automata theory','emotional','2025-03-25 14:21:01',1),(405,'assistant','It sounds like those subjects are giving you some trouble. Have you tried reaching out to your professors for guidance or seeking help from classmates?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:21:12',0),(406,'user','My classmates really don\'t care','depression','2025-03-25 14:21:21',1),(407,'assistant','I can imagine that must be tough. Remember, James, it\'s important not to compare yourself with others. Everyone has their own struggles. Have you considered speaking with your professors about your concerns?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:21:35',0),(408,'user','Do you think they will listen','extreme','2025-03-25 14:21:46',1),(409,'assistant','Absolutely! Professors are there to support and guide you. They want to see you succeed. It might be helpful to schedule a meeting with them to discuss your concerns openly. How does that sound?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:22:08',0),(410,'user','I see thanks a lot','normal','2025-03-25 14:22:14',1),(411,'assistant','You\'re welcome, James. Remember, it\'s okay to ask for help when needed. Is there anything else on your mind that you would like to talk about?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:22:32',0),(412,'user','I have been feeling anxious lately, could you please help me?','anxiety','2025-03-25 14:29:14',1),(413,'user','I have been feeling anxious lately, could you please help me?','anxiety','2025-03-25 14:32:39',1),(414,'assistant','Of course, Amit! I\'m here to support you. Can you tell me more about what\'s been making you feel anxious?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:32:54',0),(415,'user','I have my examinations coming up, and I havent really prepared','anxiety','2025-03-25 14:33:30',1),(416,'assistant','It sounds like the upcoming exams are causing you some stress. How do you usually prepare for exams, Amit?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:33:42',0),(417,'user','The problem is that I havent been doing well academically in college and I really need to increase my grades soon','depression','2025-03-25 14:34:11',1),(418,'assistant','I understand how important it is for you to perform well at college. What specific challenges are you facing with your studies?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:34:23',0),(419,'user','I am unable to do maths properly','depression','2025-03-25 14:34:33',1),(420,'assistant','Math can be challenging, but remember that everyone learns differently. Have you tried seeking help from a tutor or attending extra classes?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:34:45',0),(421,'user','I don\'t want to attend extra classes. To be honest the main cause of worry is my brother\'s performance. He is really bright and it makes me feel jealous','anxiety','2025-03-25 14:35:19',1),(422,'assistant','It can be tough comparing ourselves to others, especially when we perceive them as more successful. How do you think this comparison affects your self-esteem?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:35:36',0),(423,'user','It makes me feel bad. My parents compare me with him all the time ','depression','2025-03-25 14:35:54',1),(424,'assistant','I hear how much that hurts, Amit. Remember that everyone has their own unique strengths and talents. What are some things you enjoy doing or excel at outside of academics?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:36:10',0),(425,'user','The only thing I am good at right now is painting\\','depression','2025-03-25 14:36:23',1),(426,'assistant','Painting can be a wonderful outlet for self-expression. How does it make you feel when you engage in your artistic pursuits?\n\n',NULL,'2025-03-25 14:36:38',0),(427,'user','I feel liberated','normal','2025-03-25 14:36:43',0),(428,'assistant','Th